The paper deals with a hardware-efficient synchronization algorithm for frame timing in LTE baseband receiver design. This involves reducing the complexity of the primary synchronization signal for LTE, which is a signal processing problem. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
